query:
SELECT se.*, f.nome as formando_nome, fo.nomeRazaoSocial as fornecedor_nome
FROM servicos_execucao se
LEFT JOIN formandos f ON se.formandoId = f.id
LEFT JOIN fornecedores fo ON se.fornecedorId = fo.id
WHERE f.nome LIKE '%Ayna%'
ORDER BY se.createdAt DESC
